<div class="hero-unit round">
	<h1>About 8places</h1>
	<hr />
	<div class="text">
		<div id="service">
			<h3>Our Service</h3>
			<p>
				We make it easy to find a place to live. We do this by becoming the central hub for people who are looking for a place, and for people who have a place to rent out.<br />
				
				By providing a simple way to post houses/rooms/room-shares, we attract people who have a place to rent out. By making it easy to search for a place, we attract people who want to find a place.  
			</p>
			<div class="center">
				<%= image_tag 'finders.png', :class => "info-pics round" %>
			</div>
			<div class="center">
				<h3>Get started.</h3>
				<%= link_to "Find a Place", root_path, :class => "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
			</div>
		</div>			
		<hr />


		<div id="posters">
			<h3>Post your place to get results!</h3>
			<p>
				Do you enjoy looking for tenants? Or to look for a roommate?
				Whether you do or not, we make it easier to find that person you are looking for.
				Many people love using 8places because it is the easiest solution to finding a place to live.
				That's why it will make sense for you to post	your space on 8places.
			</p>
		
			<p>
				Posting your place on 8places is easy.
				Simply log in, click on the button on the top that says "Post a Place!"
				and some details like photos and the amount of rent. That's all you have to do! 
			</p>
			<div class="center">
				<%= image_tag 'posters.png', :class => "info-pics round" %>
			</div>
			<div class="center">
				<h3>Get started.</h3>
				<%= link_to "Post your Place", signup_path, :class => "btn btn-large btn-primary" %>
			</div>
		</div>
		<hr />
	</div>
</div>